  "prompt": "Which companies work for advertising and promotion of FlipKart?",
  "response": "Flipkart, being one of the leading e-commerce platforms in India, collaborates with various advertising and promotional agencies to enhance its brand visibility and reach. Here are some of the key agencies and companies that have worked or are working with Flipkart for advertising and promotion:\n\n1. **WPP India**: WPP is a multinational advertising and public relations company that has worked extensively with Flipkart. They handle various aspects of Flipkart's marketing, including digital marketing, creative campaigns, and media planning.\n\n2. **GroupM**: GroupM, a subsidiary of WPP, is involved in media buying and planning for Flipkart. They help in strategizing and executing media campaigns across different channels.\n\n3. **Mindshare**: Another WPP company, Mindshare, has been involved in managing Flipkart's digital marketing campaigns, ensuring that the brand's message reaches the right audience at the right time.\n\n4. **Dentsu Aegis Network**: Dentsu has worked on Flipkart's creative campaigns and has helped in crafting compelling advertisements that resonate with the target audience.\n\n5. **Publicis Groupe**: Publicis has been involved in various promotional activities for Flipkart, including social media campaigns and influencer marketing.\n\n6. **Google and Meta**: Flipkart leverages the advertising platforms of Google and Meta (formerly Facebook) for digital advertising. They run ads on Google Search, YouTube, and various social media platforms to reach a wider audience.\n\n7. **Influencer Marketing Agencies**: Flipkart also collaborates with various influencer marketing agencies to promote their products and sales events through social media influencers.\n\n8. **In-House Teams**: Flipkart has robust in-house marketing and advertising teams that work on various campaigns, especially during big sales events like The Big Billion Days.\n\nThese partnerships help Flipkart in crafting and executing comprehensive advertising and promotional strategies that contribute to its growth and market dominance.",
